data.name: libraryInfo.Text
data.value: Welcome to the Eternal Book Library, your destination for diverse and enriching reads. We're dedicated to providing Fiction, Non-Fiction, and Academic books, specifically curated to support students and teachers in their academic journey. Run by a team of 5 students from the University of Makati's College of Computing Information Sciences department. Explore the Eternal Book Library and embark on a journey of discovery with us!
